# Titanic Survival Prediction - DM Models 1

This project implements:
- Data preprocessing (handling missing values, encoding)
- Decision Tree (fine-tuned with GridSearchCV)
- Random Forest (fine-tuned with GridSearchCV)
- 5-fold cross-validation for both models

Results:
- Decision Tree Accuracy: ~0.827
- Random Forest Accuracy: ~0.833

Conclusion:
Random Forest performs slightly better due to reduced overfitting.
